---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Nico Grassetto" description="Learn more about Nico Grassetto, a web developer passionate about modern frontend technologies.">
	<section class="about-section">
		<h2 class="section-title">About</h2>
		
		<div class="about-content">
			<p>
				I'm a web developer passionate about creating thoughtful digital experiences using modern technologies. 
				I specialize in JavaScript, TypeScript, React, and various frontend frameworks and tools.
			</p>
			
			<p>
				When I'm not coding, you can find me exploring new web technologies, contributing to open source projects, 
				or sharing knowledge through writing and speaking about web development.
			</p>
			
			<p>
				This blog is where I document my learnings, share insights about web development, 
				and explore the latest trends in frontend technologies.
			</p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="contact-info">
			<h3>Get in touch</h3>
			<p>Feel free to reach out if you'd like to collaborate, have questions, or just want to say hello!</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about-content p {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}
	
	.contact-info {
		margin-top: 3rem;
		padding-top: 2rem;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
	}
	
	.contact-info h3 {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
		color: var(--text-primary);
	}
	
	.contact-info p {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
	}
</style>
